# Neural Machines Inc. ("Neural Machines", "we", "us", "our") Brand Usage Policy

## Ownership
The Neural Machines name, logo, and related brand assets are trademarks and intellectual property owned exclusively by Neural Machines.

## Permitted Use
You may use our brand assets without prior written letter for the following "Fair Use" purposes:

Editorial & News: Using the logo in a news article, blog post, or broadcast about our company.
Partners & Integrations: Using the logo to show that your product integrates with ours (e.g., "Works with Neural Machines").
Social Media: Using the logo to discuss or review our products.

## Prohibited Use
You may not do any of the following without explicit written permission from us:

Commercial Merchandise: You cannot sell t-shirts, stickers, or any physical goods featuring our logo.
Endorsement: You cannot use our logo in a way that suggests we endorse, sponsor, or are legally affiliated with your company.
Modifications: You cannot stretch, recolor, rotate, or add effects (like shadows) to our logo.
Naming: You cannot use our brand name as part of your own company name or domain name.

## No Warranties
These assets are provided "as-is." We reserve the right to revoke this permission at any time if the brand is being used in a way that we deem harmful to our reputation.

For permission requests or high-res vector files, please contact: privacy@neuralmachines.ai
